               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla samāʿtāta Ṗarāqliṭos “Vita of the Martyrs of Ṗarāqliṭos” (fols.
                     5ra-26va)
 - Introduction (fols. 5ra-6va) 
 II) Taʾammǝra samāʿtāta
                     Ṗarāqliṭos “Miracles of the Martyrs of Ṗarāqliṭos”: 11 miracles (fols.
                     27ra-54vb) 
 - Introduction (fols. 27ra-29va).</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="5ra" to="54vb"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5877DossierParaqlitos">Hagiographic Dossier of the Martyrs of Ṗarāqliṭos</title>
                     
                     <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="5ra" to="26va"/>
                        <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1491Gadlas">Gadla Ṣādǝqān za-Ṗarāqliṭos</title>
                        <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                        <note>- The explicit of Text I has been left incomplete: some words are missing
                           (cp. Ms.<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap056">AP-056</ref>, <locus target="#44va">44va</locus>).</note>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.1">
                           <locus from="5ra" to="6va"/>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1491Gadlas#Introduction">Introduction</title>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="27ra" to="54vb"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5878MiraclesParaqlitos"> Taʾammǝra samāʿtāta Ṗarāqliṭos: 11 miracles</title>
                        <textLang xml:lang="gez"/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                           <locus from="27ra" to="29va"/>
                           <title>Introduction</title>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <note>- Text II contains 11 miracles, which are not numbered; they are the same
                           and in the same sequence as in Ms.<ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESap046">AP-046</ref>.</note>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     
                     <explicit type="supplication" xml:lang="gez"><locus from="54rb" to="54vb">54rb l.10-54vb</locus></explicit>
                     
                  </msItem>
                  
               </msContents>
